channel.title: sdwdate Prerequisite check not done yet
channel.description:
One of my Whonix Gateway doesn't work anymore. It's because swdate can't do Prerequisite check. I had a issue like that before and all I need to do change time manually `sudo --set-home clock-random-manual-gui` and then run `sudo touch /run/sdwdate/first_success` I tried to do the same with this Gateway and swdate status changed to earth(like it's working) and then very fast change back to X and it's pinging X>earth>X>earth
